config SAMPLES_SENSOR_THERMOMETER_ALERT
	bool "Enable alert mode"
	default y
	help
	  Thermoter sensors generally has alarm pin too, incase of there is not or
	  you have not implemented it for your driver disable this flag
	  in your overlay file to discard alarm code from sample.

source "Kconfig.zephyr"
